class Node:

    def __init__(self, val, prev, next, child):
        self.val = val
        self.prev = prev
        self.next = next
        self.child = child

def flatten(head: 'Node') -> '':
    if not head:
        return
    pseudoHead = Node(0, None, head, None)
    prev = pseudoHead
    stack = []
    stack.append(head)
    while stack:
        curr = stack.pop()
        prev.next = curr
        curr.prev = prev
        if curr.next:
            stack.append(curr.next)
        if curr.child:
            stack.append(curr.child)
            curr.child = None
        prev = curr
    pseudoHead.next.prev = None
    return pseudoHead.next
